sequenceDiagram
  participant B as Browser (frontend-web)
  participant KC as Keycloak hosted login
  participant API as nest-api
  participant JWKS as Keycloak JWKS

  B->>KC: redirect (Auth Code + PKCE)
  KC-->>B: code → token (id+access+refresh)
  B->>API: Authorization: Bearer <jwt>
  API->>JWKS: fetch keys (cached)
  API->>API: jose.jwtVerify(token)
  API-->>B: 200 {success, data}
  Note over API: service-to-service uses<br/>client_credentials with each<br/>service's own client id/secret
